snippet.title: Johnny Depp Says Hollywood Is Boycotting Him After Amber Heard 'Wife Beater' Accusation, Libel Case
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp spoke to "The Sunday Times" to promote his new movie and said he believes his new movie is only being released in the United Kingdom, and not in the United States, because of a Hollywood boycott of him due to his ongoing legal issues.

Share your #DBLtake on #JohnnyDepp. Is he canceled?
